----------------------
 UPDATE INSTRUCTIONS
----------------------

/include/globals.php
	- Change $LAST_UPDATED, when an update is applied to this website
	- Change $WEB_ROOT variable, when website's root folder is relocated
	
/data/progress.csv 	
	- Copy updated progress.csv from project root into /data/ directory
	
/data/screenshots.csv 
	- Insert an entry into CSV file (follow the format)
	- Copy small (~ 160x100) image into /images/screenshots/small/
	- Copy large (~ 770x615) image into /images/screenshots/large/
	- ATTN: please, follow the screenshot indexing system


 
